         <supplied reason="lost">victor in Arab</supplied>ia, victor in A<supplied reason="lost">diabene</supplied>, greatest 
         <supplied reason="lost">victor in Parthia</supplied>, the Lepcitanians publicly. </p><p>b. <supplied reason="lost">To the son</supplied>
